            "body": "The docs already describe how to manually work inside an app context, as well as a method of doing this with Celery.  Flask-Script and the new CLI maintain an app context for commands.  Most tutorials also mention this.  The one thing that's missing is what you point out: a description of the error you get when something needs an app context.  I'll add this in, or welcome a PR if someone would like to contribute.\n"
